criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  They must be aged 50-90 years;

          -  Own a cell phone (ownership is > 95% in the area);

          -  Have no mobility limitations precluding routine clinic visits or bilateral blindness
             (<6/120);

          -  Be capable of giving informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Have other serious eye disease;

          -  Have mobility limitations precluding routine clinic visits or bilateral blindness
             (<6/120).
